{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.addTranslationAttr\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">addTranslationAttr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">src</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">cfg</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">kind</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Attributes.html#Lean.AttributeKind\">Lean.AttributeKind</a> := <a href=\"./Lean/Attributes.html#Lean.AttributeKind.global\">Lean.AttributeKind.global</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Attributes.html#Lean.AttrM\">Lean.AttrM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`addTranslationAttr src cfg` adds a translation attribute to `src` with configuration `cfg`.\nSee the attribute implementation for more details.\nIt returns an array with names of translated declarations (usually 1, but more if there are nested\n`to_additive` calls). ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.addTranslationAttr","kind":"opaque","line":1276,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.addTranslationAttr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L1276-L1312"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.copyMetaData\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">copyMetaData</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">cfg</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">src</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">Lean.CoreM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Copies equation lemmas and attributes from `src` to `tgt`\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.copyMetaData","kind":"opaque","line":1255,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.copyMetaData","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L1255-L1274"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.applyAttributes\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">applyAttributes</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">cfg</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">src </span><span class=\"fn\">tgt</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">reorder</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Reorder\">Reorder</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">relevantArg</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.RelevantArg\">RelevantArg</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Term/TermElabM.html#Lean.Elab.Term.TermElabM\">Lean.Elab.TermElabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Apply attributes to the original and translated declarations. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.applyAttributes","kind":"opaque","line":1187,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.applyAttributes","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L1187-L1253"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.elabTranslationAttr\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabTranslationAttr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Lean.Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">Lean.CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config\">Config</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Elaboration of the configuration options for a translation attribute. It is assumed that\n- `stx[0]` is the attribute (e.g. `to_additive`)\n- `stx[1]` is the optional tracing `?`\n- `stx[2]` is the remaining `attrArgs`\n\nTODO: Currently, we don't deduce any `dont_translate` arguments based on the type of `declName`.\nIn the future we would like that the presence of `MonoidAlgebra k G` will automatically\nflag `k` as a type to not be translated. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.elabTranslationAttr","kind":"def","line":1094,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.elabTranslationAttr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L1094-L1184"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.elabArgStx\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabArgStx</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=