ion dictionary. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config.attrs","kind":"def","line":312,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config.attrs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L312-L312"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config.relevantArg?\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">relevantArg?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.RelevantArg\">RelevantArg</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The argument used to determine whether this constant should be translated. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config.relevantArg?","kind":"def","line":309,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config.relevantArg?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L309-L309"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.Config.reorder?\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">reorde