"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The name of the attribute, for example `to_additive` or `to_dual`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.attrName","kind":"def","line":219,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.attrName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L219-L219"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.translations\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">TranslateData</span>.<span class=\"name\">translations</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Lean/NameMapAttribute.html#Lean.NameMapExtension\">Lean.NameMapExtension</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslationInfo\">TranslationInfo</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`translations` stores all of the constants that have been tagged with this attribute,\nand maps them to their translation. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.translations","kind":"def","line":217,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.translations","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L217-L217"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.unfoldBoundaries?\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">TranslateData</span>.<span class=\"name\">unfoldBoundaries?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/UnfoldBoundary.html#Mathlib.Tactic.UnfoldBoundary.UnfoldBoundaryExt\">UnfoldBoundary.UnfoldBoundaryExt</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The `insert_cast`/`insert_cast_fun` attributes create an abstraction boundary for the tagged\nconstant when translating it. For example, `Set.Icc`, `Monotone`, `DecidableLT`, `WCovBy` are all\nmorally self-dual, but their definition is not self-dual. So, in order to allow these constants\nto be self-dual, we need to not unfold their definition in the proof term that we translate. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.unfoldBoundaries?","kind":"def","line":214,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.unfoldBoundaries?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L214-L214"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.doTranslateAttr\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">TranslateData</span>.<span class=\"name\">doTranslateAttr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Lean/NameMapAttribute.html#Lean.NameMapExtension\">Lean.NameMapExtension</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The global `do_translate`/`dont_translate` attributes specify whether operations on\na given type should be translated. `dont_translate` can be used for types that are translated,\nsuch as `MonoidAlgebra` -> `AddMonoidAlgebra`, or for fixed types, such as `Fin n`/`ZMod n`.\n`do_translate` is for types without arguments, like `Unit` and `Empty`, where the structure on it\ncan be translated.\n\nNote: The name generation is not aware of `dont_translate`, so if some part of a lemma is not\n  translated thanks to this, you generally have to specify the translated name manually.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.doTranslateAttr","kind":"def","line":209,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.doTranslateAttr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L209-L209"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.ignoreArgsAttr\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">TranslateData</span>.<span class=\"name\">ignoreArgsAttr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Lean/NameMapAttribute.html#Lean.NameMapExtension\">Lean.NameMapExtension</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"An attribute that tells that certain arguments of this definition are not\ninvolved when translating.\nThis helps the translation heuristic by also transforming definitions if `ℕ` or another\nfixed type occurs as one of these arguments. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.ignoreArgsAttr","kind":"def","line":199,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.ignoreArgsAttr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L199-L199"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Translate</span>.<span class=\"name\">TranslateData</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ignoreArgsAttr</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Lean/NameMapAttribute.html#Lean.NameMapExtension\">Lean.NameMapExtension</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">doTranslateAttr</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Lean/NameMapAttribute.html#Lean.NameMapExtension\">Lean.NameMapExtension</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">unfoldBoundaries?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/UnfoldBoundary.html#Mathlib.Tactic.UnfoldBoundary.UnfoldBoundaryExt\">UnfoldBoundary.UnfoldBoundaryExt</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">translations</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Lean/NameMapAttribute.html#Lean.NameMapExtension\">Lean.NameMapExtension</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslationInfo\">TranslationInfo</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">attrName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">changeNumeral </span><span class=\"fn\">isDual</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">guessNameData</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/GuessName.html#Mathlib.Tactic.GuessName.GuessNameData\">GuessName.GuessNameData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData\">TranslateData</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.mk","kind":"ctor","line":194,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Translate.TranslateData.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Tactic/Translate/Core.lean#L194-L194"}},{"hea